Luv 0.1dev
==========

Luv is Lua (lua.org) MVC web-framework. Luv is open-source and 
completely free for both commercial and non-commercial use.

Luv is:
- much faster then any PHP, Ruby, or Python frameworks;
- simple and flexible API;
- complete solution for any web-service.

Luv includes:
- Prototype-based OOP;
- Exceptions;
- CGI lib;
- Unit-testing libs;
- "Tamplier" template engine written in pure Lua;
- MVC (Validators, Fields, Models, Forms);
- URL conf;
- Widgets;
- ... will be much more soon ...

What's new
==========

Version 0.1dev
--------------
+ Basic OOP and exceptions; 
+ CGI interface;
+ Development version of Tamplier template engine;
+ Unit-testing framework. 

